Package: scalingPlantArchitecture
Title: Scaling Plant Architecture Under WBE-Inspired Branching
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Brian", "Jenquist", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "author@example.com")
Description: Simulates asymmetric branching trees with variable path lengths,
    draws Smith-style architecture figures, and computes analytical and
    simulation-based scaling implications in a WBE-inspired framework.
